title: How to Install a Hunter Ceiling Fan - 5xxxx Series Models
description:
A new ceiling fan is a simple way to improve how your home looks and feels. See step-by-step how easy it is to assemble and install a ceiling fan. 

This video will take you step-by-step through the installation process that is outlined in your Owner's Manual. While each fan may have unique components specific to its installation, this video applies to most Hunter "5xxxx" series model numbers.
